# Task

The verification pipeline needs ONE document describing the INTENDED BEHAVIOR and INVARIANTS of the
contract under analysis — what the system is supposed to do, so the Certora Prover can check the
implementation against it. Locate the single best EXISTING such document in this project, or honestly
report that none exists.

# Tools

